&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Aperia, we rely on a dynamic team of developers. We’re seeking a Business Analyst who is ready to work with new technologies and architectures in a forward-thinking organization that’s always pushing boundaries.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We are looking for a person to join our team in a critical role of the Business Analyst.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will work with our internal client defining and refining the business needs into actionable user stores and tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working directly for the Delivery Lead / Product Owner, you will serve a liaison between Client team, Development team and Data Warehouse team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be instrumental in data identification, data analysis, unit testing and managing user testing &amp;amp; sign off.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We are looking for someone with attention to detail, a sense of ownership, good interpersonal skills and excellent documentation skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your work will increase efficiency in the development process and reduce exceptions / bugs / test failures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;QUALIFICATIONS&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A Bachelor’s degree in a computer or engineering discipline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5 years of experience as a Business Analyst&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid knowledge of SDLC (Waterfall) and Agile development methodologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong ability to transform / extract required details from higher level business requests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of query language such as SQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High level of comfort in excel / access manipulating data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A solid understanding of testing and test case development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Skills, Experience, and Education: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of JAVA, Angular&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of prototyping applications such as Axure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Copilot&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
